metadata.name: Catch of The Day - Cartagena, Colombia
metadata.description:
Catch of the day,

Two herons plan the wind, they await the courtship of a third that seduces the man as if she were dancing her wings to the sound of Caribbean cumbias and African drums that she hears from the radios of other fishermen.

This artisanal fisherman from Cartagena (Colombia) returns from the morning shift, and finishes his ancestral trade, sharing his precious loot to catch friends who accompany him daily at the end of his sunny workday.

(2015 - Cartagena, Colombia)
